Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}貴方以上なんていないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}You're my missing piece
